## Extending Your Configuration

axiOS is a **desktop system framework**. For additional services (web servers, databases, IoT platforms), add them in your `extraConfig`:

\`\`\`nix
extraConfig = {
  # Import your own modules
  imports = [ ./my-services.nix ];
  
  # Or configure services directly
  services.postgresql.enable = true;
  services.nginx.virtualHosts."example.com" = { ... };
};
\`\`\`

See [NixOS Options](https://search.nixos.org/options) for available services.

**Note:** axiOS provides desktop tools and development environment. Server services are outside the scope of this framework.

